-- Besiktas in Talks With Banks for $85 Million Loan, Sabah Says
-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 2012-07-25T08:52:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-25/besiktas-in-talks-with-banks-for-85-million-loan-sabah-says.html
Besiktas Futbol Yatirimlari Sanayi &
Ticaret AS (BJKAS) , the merchandising unit of Turkish sports club
Besiktas, is in talks with banks for an $85 million loan,  Sabah 
reported, without saying where it got the information.  Part of the loan will be used to repay $50 million of
outstanding debt and for overdue payments, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
 eersoy@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net  